{"tid":1267610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄺囝：讓我們好好互相扶持，不再有多一位手足出事","createTime":"2019-06-30T03:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T05:36:48.000Z","uid":179648,"like":41,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"735fd5b691494d8ae837c6930dd4148aff98f14a","tid":1267610,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"唔好再有下一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rxTo1et.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrxTo1et.jpg&h=fbc6ddd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qwp7JsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqwp7JsT.jpg&h=5198d619&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d4b2d37abb1f9db41622581c2f33b10214177c7","tid":1267610,"uid":179648,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:37:02.000Z","msg":"《我們都是一個人》鄺俊宇<br />\n<br />\n知道你真的很傷心，我明白，因為我和你一樣，心裡像有一個碰不到的傷口，傷口會痛，卻找不到紓緩痛楚的出口。<br />\n<br />\n知道嗎？心裡若有痛的感覺就得要說出來，放聲哭一場也沒壞，眼淚能夠承載你的痛苦，至少你願意承認自己的脆弱，別忘記，我們都是一個人，堅強有時、脆弱有時；也別忘記，我們不只是一個人，因為有很多陪著你走的朋友，他們每一位都疼你，只要你願意講，他們隨傳隨到來到你的身邊。<br />\n<br />\n我們不能再承受多一位手足出事了，答應我們，好好珍惜自己好嗎？青春本來很精彩，但若為了那一個冷血的強權而劃上休止符，那就萬萬的不值得，知道嗎？還有很多的精彩在未來等著我們，除了是我們的夢想、除了是我們的人生，還有期待著某一天若我們勝利歸來，舉杯時，希望我們都齊齊整整，一個都不能少。<br />\n<br />\n你懂我的，你懂我在寫這篇文章時，怎樣一邊流淚一邊寫。連日來，無論我與你有沒有相遇過，我都真心把你當作我們的手足，因為你受傷，我們會痛；因為你流血，我們會痛；因為你出事，我們會傷心。所以請應承我們，有事要找朋友說，眼淚找對人來哭就有意義。<br />\n<br />\n我們都是一個人，但我們不只是一個人。<br />\n<br />\n讓我們好好互相扶持，不再有多一位手足出事，就像梁生和梁太的叮囑：<br />\n<br />\n「我們每一次都要平平安安、安安全全的回家。」<br />\n<br />\n手足們，七一見。"},{"pid":"ed9041565446ba58d784891f76af68a4cd9be8a9","tid":1267610,"uid":23169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:37:29.000Z","msg":"鄺囝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a6303790ce041107485f26337f392e645b9613","tid":1267610,"uid":5680,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FVhdD2v.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFVhdD2v.gif&h=1f8249ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efdb2e2d3eecd5a5002e1498272557d9e1cd1da4","tid":1267610,"uid":18639,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:39:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0mPvCY3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0mPvCY3.png&h=40f89ffe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e739b2a5ef5b0e92c3cbda8f705a68a6387f413b","tid":1267610,"uid":69960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:39:25.000Z","msg":"一個都不能再少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf33740333a0ba10d79096c2fb214fc733e15bb","tid":1267610,"uid":179648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:40:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41e3847d98ed2416a0972cca5e7a5b7b27c7e2f0","tid":1267610,"uid":87901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8134c35465266cbfc84a3d97d928611ea2c83628","tid":1267610,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"鄺仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e713ebaf7f32647cb51efefd21d38469cfb5edd","tid":1267610,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:19:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3058ff3658b7801b51634bb163d6ce872f2176f0","tid":1267610,"uid":66639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\